{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a20a3eee65","title":"右派言论——“不要马列主义”","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2a90480070","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"a20a3eee65"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"79af059482","name":"山西师范学院"},{"id":"8fb6588f9f","name":"田雨翔"},{"id":"df7b563558","name":"汪子云"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"39eb14361f","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“不要马列主义”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"},{"id":"8530c2b303","type":"authors","text":"山西师范学院汪子云田雨翔","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"},{"id":"6a1c54849c","type":"paragraph","text":"汪子云（山西师范学院教授、九三学社社员）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"},{"id":"4cf72ea0d1","type":"paragraph","text":"“不要马列主义，不学马列主义照样能把古典文学学好，我就不学马列主义”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"},{"id":"c8d1a182fc","type":"paragraph","text":"田雨翔（山西师范学院教授、民盟省筹委组织部长）：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"},{"id":"5ad1a388fc","type":"paragraph","text":"“马列主义有什么学头，不过就是那几条，由人家（指我们）变，今天左，明天右，奇妙莫测；我只晓得庄子哲学，进攻之先，退避三舍，观察动静，再向前攻”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"},{"id":"e50d35642b","type":"paragraph","text":"“知识分子就是为知识而斗争，如果我们没有一套，共产党才不要你呢，这也是利用、限制、改造，只要有被人利用之处就不怕。向科学进军就是显示我们能力的机会。共产党对我们知识分子就是不信任，不要说三顾茅庐，只要少斗争点就好了”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"},{"id":"4c750e6f14","type":"paragraph","text":"“政治舞台就是唱戏，谁唱的好，谁就成功”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65"}],"page":{"id":"2ff864a940","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a20a3eee65","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}